          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25139688/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25139688/" class="">第14页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Ahasver/" class=" " title="Ahasver">Ahasver</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25139688">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我试图做的是（⋯⋯）标定和分析那个利用这些话语并试图使它们运转的权力技术，而不是企图进行意识形态分析或“制度主义”（institutionnaliste）分析。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-14 12:46</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>我试图做的是（⋯⋯）标定和分析那个利用这些话语并试图使它们运转的权力技术，而不是企图进行意识形态分析或“制度主义”（institutionnaliste）分析。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25139688/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2013-03-14 12:46
                </div>
